  "2026-06-21T21:20:49.034Z",claude-code-agent,"Evidence: implemented package/extension init --capability commands|hooks. Hook scaffolds declare commands+hooks, register a starter command plus after_command lifecycle hook, emit package-mode SDK sample tests with assertRegisteredHook/runRegisteredHookForTest, expose capability in init results/help/completions/contracts, and reject --capability on non-init actions. Verification passed: focused test bundle 421 tests; pnpm build && pnpm contracts:check; pnpm quality:static; pnpm security:scan; manual temp smoke at /tmp/tmp.2DM5gLYLNL with npm test, pm install, package doctor deep trace status ok warning_count 0, and pm hook-package ping; node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage passed literal 100/100/100/100 across 4,830 tests."
